  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Control AI Before it Controls You</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ESCAPE CONDITION is the first game that lets you take control of society's future amidst the AI revolution. Use messages from the Future Resistance to identify the AI Branches that will change your world - then decide the fate of each branch. <br><br><br>Choose how technology should advance - are machines meant to be our masters or our slaves?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391580/extras/4d8eb75b4b6a1b34bee3681153624ff8.avif?t=1772297496\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose how chaotic society should be - is power meant to be centralized or decentralized?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391580/extras/6ec2e6834f56b63fe33af0a57515887c.avif?t=1772297496\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose how humanity should pursue immortality - physical pursuits pollute the world, digital pursuits reduce quality of life</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391580/extras/1b970d743d9daf1a867b197cc9cbb8ec.avif?t=1772297496\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Control AI Before it Controls You</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ESCAPE CONDITION is the first game that lets you take control of society's future amidst the AI revolution. Use messages from the Future Resistance to identify the AI Branches that will change your world - then decide the fate of each branch. <br><br><br>Choose how technology should advance - are machines meant to be our masters or our slaves?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391580/extras/4d8eb75b4b6a1b34bee3681153624ff8.avif?t=1772297496\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose how chaotic society should be - is power meant to be centralized or decentralized?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391580/extras/6ec2e6834f56b63fe33af0a57515887c.avif?t=1772297496\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose how humanity should pursue immortality - physical pursuits pollute the world, digital pursuits reduce quality of life</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391580/extras/1b970d743d9daf1a867b197cc9cbb8ec.avif?t=1772297496\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
